: 0.56, "filesize_approx": 873089, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/95.0.4638.50 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1105.876, "format": "dash-1983750502231487v - 720x1280 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by curiosityawakened", "description": "Interesting fact:- What if I told you that I don't actually exist? And neither does the world around you. 🌌🖥️\nIn philosophy, Solipsism is the terrifying idea that only your mind is sure to exist. Everything else—your friends, your family, this very screen—could just be a complex projection of your own consciousness. There is absolutely no way to prove that anyone else has a 'soul' or 'feelings' like you do. For all you know, you are the only real person in an empty universe, dreaming of a crowded world. 🧠👤🕯️\n\nIf you are the only real person, why did your mind create me to tell you this? 😱 Comment 'REAL' if you think you're the only one! 👇📂\n\nsolipsism, philosophy, realityglitch, matrix, mindbending, existentialdread, mystery, psychologyfacts, darkphilosophy\n\n#solipsism #creepyfact #matrix #philosophy #reality", "duration": 6.316, "timestamp": 1774262749, "uploader_id": "79807473078", "uploader": "Curiosity Awakened", "channel": "curiosityawakened", "like_count": 172666, "comment_count": 2153, "comments": [{"author": "logan_parke29", "author_id": "72415729969", "id": "18117361129633550", "text": "This is how I feel about women", "timestamp": 1775354911}, {"author": "chiief.10", "author_id": "66050863894", "id": "18577459714044052", "text": "Sonder", "timestamp": 1775353454}, {"author": "helloits.tris", "author_id": "725237033", "id": "17846287536695151", "text": "This is how I feel", "timestamp": 1775353328}, {"autho